WEBVTT

00:02:29.826 --> 00:02:32.135
Kama wamechungulia au la,

00:02:32.159 --> 00:02:35.211
watoto waliochungulia watakiri

00:02:35.235 --> 00:02:37.813
au watadanganya kuhusu makosa yao?

00:02:39.525 --> 00:02:44.298
Tuligundua kwamba bila kujali
jinsia, nchi, au dini,

00:02:44.934 --> 00:02:46.513
katika umri wa miaka miwili,

00:02:47.188 --> 00:02:49.115
asilimia 30 hudanganya,

00:02:49.139 --> 00:02:52.948
asilimia 70 husema ukweli
kuhusu makosa yao.

00:02:52.972 --> 00:02:55.110
Katika umri wa miaka mitatu,

00:02:55.134 --> 00:02:58.608
asilimia 50 hudanganya na asilimia 50
husema kweli.

00:02:59.302 --> 00:03:01.201
Katika umri wa miaka minne,